languages.text: В последние месяцы перед смертью бредящий Денз говорил о "мертвых глазах", смотрящих на него.
In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

languages.text: 在丹兹死前的最后几个月里，曾大吵大嚷说有“死人的眼睛”在盯着他。
languages.original_text: In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

traits.locale_text: 在丹兹死前的最后几个月里，曾大吵大嚷说有“死人的眼睛”在盯着他。

languages.text: 死の数カ月前、デンツは彼を見つめる「死んだ目」についてうわごとを言っていた。
languages.original_text: In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

traits.locale_text: 死の数カ月前、デンツは彼を見つめる「死んだ目」についてうわごとを言っていた。

languages.text: En sus últimos meses de vida, Denz hablaba de unos «ojos muertos» que le observaban.
languages.original_text: In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

traits.locale_text: En sus últimos meses de vida, Denz hablaba de unos «ojos muertos» que le observaban.

languages.text: In den letzten Monaten vor seinem Tod behauptete Denz, er würde von "toten Augen" beobachtet.
languages.original_text: In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

traits.locale_text: In den letzten Monaten vor seinem Tod behauptete Denz, er würde von "toten Augen" beobachtet.

languages.text: Dans les mois qui ont précédé sa mort, Denz délirait à propos d'« yeux morts » qui le fixaient.
languages.original_text: In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

traits.locale_text: Dans les mois qui ont précédé sa mort, Denz délirait à propos d'« yeux morts » qui le fixaient.

languages.text: Denz, ölmeden önceki son aylarında onu izleyen "ölü gözler" hakkında sayıklıyormuş.
languages.original_text: In the last months before his death, Denz raved about "dead eyes" watching him.

traits.locale_text: Ölümü öncesindeki son aylarda Denz, onu izleyen "ölü gözler" hakkında sayıklıyormuş.
